metadata.name: The Great Magnetic Field of Cheetos
metadata.description: An engineered Cheeto loop which is the cure for the marriage of Apollonian and Dionysian art. Just out of your reach, this Pavlovian stringer will keep your MSG flowing to tickle your Brain Flowers. This is Nobody when he is soupy faced and looking into the Void. An early Resemblag√® first published in 2017, so please chew with your mouth closed.
